CHARLES WENRICH v. STATE OF FLORIDA 32 So. (2nd) 12

June Term, 1947

October 3, 1947 Special Division B Manuel M. Glover, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and Reeves Bowen, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. *495PER CURIAM:

On authority of the opinion and judgment in Charles Wen-rich v. State of Florida (Number 7341) this day filed, the judgment in this appeal is

Reversed.

THOMAS, C. J., TERRELL, ADAMS and BARNS, JJ., concur.
